data.description: Adorable and tastefully updated 2 bedroom, 2 bath home with bonus room, near schools and shopping. Laminate flooring in kitchen, living room and bedrooms, tile in both bathrooms. Beautiful front and back yard with drought resistant landscaping and mature fruit trees that provide shade and privacy. Home has dual pane windows, 2 mini-split units for heat/AC and a gas wall heater.
